data.value: First, As you can see in the screenshot shown to you now, you must first choose the file that you want to change its format, let it be a JPEG file and you want to convert it to PNG only. After you have selected the file, choose the format from the formats in front of you, then click on the (Convert) button and it will take a few seconds and you will receive a message that the process was successful and then the file saving interface
